input_args.pipeline:
Pipeline(memory=FastMemory(location=./caching_directory/joblib),
         steps=[('date_feature_extractor',
                 TransformerWrapper(include=['Created', 'Deleted'],
                                    transformer=ExtractDateTimeFeatures(features=['weekday',
                                                                                  'day',
                                                                                  'hour',
                                                                                  'minute']))),
                ('numerical_imputer',
                 TransformerWrapper(include=['MAX CPU', 'AVG CPU',
                                             '95th Percentile(MAX CPU)',
                                             'Diff 1', 'Diff 2',
                                             'Life Time (Hour...
                 TransformerWrapper(include=['VM Type'],
                                    transformer=OneHotEncoder(cols=['VM Type'],
                                                              handle_missing='return_nan',
                                                              use_cat_names=True))),
                ('rest_encoding',
                 TransformerWrapper(include=['Subscription ID',
                                             'Deployment ID'],
                                    transformer=CountEncoder(cols=['Subscription '
                                                                   'ID',
                                                                   'Deployment '
                                                                   'ID'],
                                                             combine_min_nan_groups=True))),
                ('normalize', TransformerWrapper(transformer=MinMaxScaler()))])
